<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.9">
<l>kommai mulaikaḷiṭar tīrak kōvintaṟ kōr kuṟṟēval</l>
<l>immaip piṟavi ceyyātē yiṉippōyc ceyyun tavantāṉeṉ</l>
<l>cemmai yuṭaiya tirumārviṟ cērttā ṉēlu moruñāṉṟu</l>
<l>meymmai colli mukanōkki viṭaitāṉ ṟarumēl mikanaṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What for a penance that one performs going [to the next world] now,</l>
<l rend="indent">Not performing menial service in this birth</l>
<l>For Govinda, so that the distress of [my] youthful breasts end?</l>
<l>If He draws [me] against [His] excellent, auspicious chest, [good!]</l>
<l>If some day, He speaks the truth and gives me a reply looking at [my] face, very good indeed!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
